{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel.name","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><em><code>name</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>BroadcastChannel.name</strong></code> 是类型为 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 的只读属性，是频道的唯一标识。属性 name 是在创建时传入 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\" title=\"BroadcastChannel()\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a> 构造函数的，所以是只读的。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 此特性在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 中可用</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>str</em> = <em>channe<code>l</code></em><code>.name;</code>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 连接到指定频道</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'test_channel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 其它操作 (如：postMessage, …)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 在控制台打印频道名称</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"test_channel\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 当完成后，断开与频道的连接</span>\nbc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-messaging.html#dom-broadcastchannel-name-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.name"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.name","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":nu